HEADWORD: Unparagoned
<hw>Un*par"a*goned</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no
paragon or equal; matchless; peerless.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Your <qex>unparagoned</qex> mistress is dead.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unparalleled</ent>⟦br⟧
